00:13:07.757 --> 00:13:09.590
Polished to, I think,
somewhere in the order

00:13:09.590 --> 00:13:12.280
of a few nanometers
mean surface roughness.

00:13:12.280 --> 00:13:14.800
Using a chemical mechanical
polishing mechanism.

00:13:14.800 --> 00:13:18.840
The thickness is around
