00:16:59.490 --> 00:17:01.590
Multicrystalline silicon.

00:17:01.590 --> 00:17:03.110
Let's put it this way for now.

00:17:03.110 --> 00:17:05.026
We'll describe how
multicrystalline silicon is

00:17:05.026 --> 00:17:06.569
